name: Bad Sisters
overview: The tight-knit Garvey sisters have always looked out for one another. But when the toxic brother-in-law they all wanted dead actually dies, it turns their lives upside down and tests their bond like nothing before.

seasons.name: Season 2
seasons.overview: Two years after the "accidental death" of Grace's abusive husband, the close-knit Garvey sisters may have moved on, but when past truths resurface, the ladies are thrust back into the spotlight, suspicions are at an all-time high, lies are told, secrets are revealed and the sisters are forced to work out who they can trust.

episodes.name: The Prick
episodes.overview: John Paul is dead. The Garvey sisters think it's all behind them—but the insurance men have questions.

episodes.name: Explode a Man
episodes.overview: As Thomas and Matt grasp at straws in the present, a sinister plot takes shape in the past.

episodes.name: Chopped Liver
episodes.overview: Ursula is next in John Paul's crosshairs. Thomas hopes the police will help him.

episodes.name: Baby Becka
episodes.overview: Becka comes to regret trusting John Paul. In the present, she and Matt get a shock.

episodes.name: Eye for an Eye
episodes.overview: Bibi is gripped by a bold, dangerous idea for John Paul's birthday. Matt learns a difficult truth.

episodes.name: Splash
episodes.overview: The Garvey sisters regroup as their fears grow for Grace's well-being. Thomas finally gets a lead.

episodes.name: Rest in Peace
episodes.overview: John Paul suspects foul play as he pieces together what happened. Thomas and Matt reconnect.

episodes.name: The Cold Truth
episodes.overview: Becka is determined to prove Eva wrong. Thomas and Matt wait for news of a breakthrough.

episodes.name: Going Rogue
episodes.overview: The sisters get a heartbreaking reality check. Matt steps up as Thomas begins to crumble.
